PRO_LIFE conference
-------------------
From: Jon Guidry (1:3803/11.1701)

Hello to all your sysops (and users) out there.  :) There's
always room in FIDOnet for another conference, so I'm launching
a PRO_LIFE conference.

I know some of you might REALLY want this conference, and some
may "blast" me, as the PRO_LIFE issue is a very touchy subject.
As moderator of R_CATHOLIC, I see to it that peaceful discussion
that actually yields some- thing takes place. I don't allow
uncontrolled arguing and "bashing" inside R_CATHOLIC, and won't
allow it in PRO_LIFE.

PRO_LIFE is a conference that anybody concerned about the
Pro-Life move- ment can join. Whether you are Roman Catholic,
Methodist, etc, if you support the cause of life, you are more
than welcome to join this conference.

