Alex Mottram @ 1:3803/16 may be contacted for feeds.  If he
doesn't respond right away, feel free to mail him more than
once, as he is very busy.

R_CATHOLIC and PRO_LIFE are also linked to the  Catholic
Information Network, which is hosted by Mike Molleurus at
1:202/1613.

Again, thanks for your support. When I put R_CATHOLIC in the
E-list, and sent in the submission to FIDOSTAT.NA, I really got
support from the REC's.

Thanks!
Jon (1:3803/11.1701)

